    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document provides information for the novice Internet user about using the File Transfer Protocol (FTP).  It explains what FTP is, what anonymous FTP is, and what an anonymous FTP archive site is.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
